                                            <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
                                            Cancelled
                                        </span>
                                        Reason: Not good Taste
                                        
                                  
                                        <span class="badge bg-success">
                                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                            Returned
                                        </span>
                                        Reason : Not good Taste

                                        
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary">
                                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i>
                                            Return Request
                                        </span>
